From here on out Jour will now go by the name Alan Mind. Why the change Well we ve joined forces with the European healthcare provider Alan. Together we re working to make mental health care as accessible and accepted as physical health care.

Drumroll please! Cause we have another big change this week! We ve listened to all your feedback all the messages you sent us and we re excited to add 7 new options to your Daily Journal check in! 1. Pet for the fluffier friends in your life 2. News because wow did we watch a lot of news this year 3. Injustice so that journalers facing discrimination or fighting for social justice can fully express how they re feeling and find guided journals for what they re facing 4. Self Talk because sometimes what really affects us is how we think to ourselves 5. School to be more inclusive for students and our younger journalers 6. Weather because science has proved the weather has a real effect on how you feel 7. Other just in case we haven t included an option that reflects what s affecting you today! We hope that these new options help you create a space that more fully reflects your life and in return provides you with the guidance and support that you re looking for.
